title: Fitch Revises Taiwan's Eximbank's Outlook to Positive on Sovereign Action (Fitch Inc)
text: ( Source : Fitch Inc) 19 Oct 2015 2:28 AM GMT / UTC Fitch Ratings-Taipei-19 October 2015 : Fitch Ratings has today revised the Outlook on The Export-Import Bank of the Republic of China (Taiwan 's Eximbank ) to Positive from Stable and affirmed
